dataIdInfo.idPurp: 2021-22 Catchment boundaries for the School District of Philadelphia elementary schools. Date updated: 5/9/2022. Metadata updated: 5/9/2022.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Data prepared by the School District of Philadelphia, Office of Capital Programs. Timothy Lambert, tlambert@philasd.org.
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Boundary delineation for all catchment elementary schools within the School District of Philadelphia. 'Neighborhood' schools utilize these boundaries to determine where students will be assigned. Special admission schools, which use different admission criteria, are excluded from this file.

Key Attribute Fields:

ES_ID : Catchment elementary school ID.

ES_Name : Catchment elementary school name.

MS_ID : Catchment middle school ID.

MS_Name : Catchment middle school name.

HS_ID : Catchment high school ID.

HS_Name : Catchment high school name.

Gr_ID_K : Catchment school ID for kindergarten.

GR_ID_01 : Catchment school ID for 1st grade.

GR_ID_02 : Catchment school ID for 2nd grade.

GR_ID_03 : Catchment school ID for 3rd grade.

GR_ID_04 : Catchment school ID for 4th grade.

GR_ID_05 : Catchment school ID for 5th grade.

GR_ID_06 : Catchment school ID for 6th grade.

GR_ID_07 : Catchment school ID for 7th grade.

GR_ID_08 : Catchment school ID for 8th grade.

GR_ID_10 : Catchment school ID for 10th grade.

GR_ID_11 : Catchment school ID for 11th grade.

GR_ID_12 : Catchment school ID for 12th grade.

ES_Grade : Catchment elementary school grade range.

ES_Level ; Catchment elementary school level.

MS_Grade : Catchment middle school grade range.
